814
01:15:55,058 --> 01:15:57,143
JIM: What you want to do
about these pigs?

815
01:16:03,900 --> 01:16:06,402
FITZGERALD:
The Lord's on our side, kid.

816
01:16:14,744 --> 01:16:16,329
FITZGERALD:
You all right there, kid?

817
01:16:16,662 --> 01:16:18,581
Your head in the right place?

818
01:16:19,248 --> 01:16:20,583
I guess.

819
01:16:25,671 --> 01:16:28,341
I can't help thinking about
whether we did the right--

820
01:16:28,674 --> 01:16:30,927
Ain't our place to wonder.
The good Lord...

821
01:16:31,010 --> 01:16:34,263
...got us on a road
whether we choose it or not.

822
01:16:37,517 --> 01:16:40,770
My pop, he weren't
a religious man, you know?

823
01:16:40,853 --> 01:16:43,022
If you couldn't grow it,
kill it, or eat it,

824
01:16:43,106 --> 01:16:46,025
he just plain old
didn't believe in it.

825
