876
01:27:12,860 --> 01:27:14,653
A bear.

877
01:27:15,696 --> 01:27:17,489
A bear.

878
01:27:18,490 --> 01:27:20,117
Grizzly.

879
01:27:23,328 --> 01:27:24,830
Grizzly.

880
01:27:38,010 --> 01:27:41,847
My men... left me for dead.

881
01:27:42,723 --> 01:27:45,309
Killed my son.

882
01:27:48,353 --> 01:27:53,358
I lost my family too.

883
01:27:53,734 --> 01:27:56,361
Sioux killed my people.

884
01:27:57,529 --> 01:28:04,495
I'm going south to find more Pawnee.

885
01:28:07,748 --> 01:28:11,293
My heart bleeds...

886
01:28:12,753 --> 01:28:16,673
But revenge is in the creator's hands.

887
