895
01:30:00,152 --> 01:30:03,155
FITZGERALD: Yeah!
There she is.

896
01:30:04,615 --> 01:30:05,991
We did it.

897
01:30:06,992 --> 01:30:09,494
You ought to be
proud of yourself, boy.

898
01:30:10,412 --> 01:30:11,455
Yeah.

899
