the funeral part.

901
01:30:15,334 --> 01:30:18,795
Don't go down there
and start growing
no conscience.

902
01:30:19,004 --> 01:30:20,088
'Cause sure
as night'll come

903
01:30:20,172 --> 01:30:22,758
they'll have us swinging
from a couple ropes.

904
01:30:22,841 --> 01:30:25,510
We did
what we had to do.

905
