908
01:30:53,205 --> 01:30:55,540
FITZGERALD:
We had the extra day
So we managed to dig...

909
01:30:55,832 --> 01:30:57,376
...a little deeper,
lay rocks on top

910
01:30:57,459 --> 01:30:59,002
SO scavengers
couldn't get at him.

911
01:30:59,169 --> 01:31:02,381
It was done right and all.
He was buried right.

912
01:31:03,715 --> 01:31:04,967
Sir, can we--

913
01:31:05,050 --> 01:31:06,259
The truth is that...

914
01:31:06,343 --> 01:31:07,636
