to move on out.

917
01:31:14,559 --> 01:31:18,397
Yeah, but, Bridger here
argued to stay.

918
01:31:19,231 --> 01:31:21,358
He argued to stay...

919
01:31:21,441 --> 01:31:24,444
...S0 he could at least
build a cross or something...

920
01:31:24,903 --> 01:31:26,488
...to put on top
of Glass's grave,

921
01:31:26,571 --> 01:31:29,574
and that's what he did.
That's what we did.

922
01:31:29,658 --> 01:31:32,119
I'm glad you pulled
your weight, Mr. Bridger.

923
01:31:32,202 --> 01:31:33,829
