pulled his weight, Captain.

924
01:31:33,912 --> 01:31:36,331
This man here,
he was my partner.

925
01:31:42,421 --> 01:31:46,383
Am I to assume that
the agreed arrangement
did not change?

926
01:31:46,466 --> 01:31:49,344
Uh, fortunately for me,
it did not.

927
01:31:49,428 --> 01:31:50,971
HENRY: Mmm-hmm.

928
01:31:57,728 --> 01:31:59,938
