929
01:32:11,283 --> 01:32:12,784
Thank you...

930
01:32:13,118 --> 01:32:17,122
...for your courage,
honor, and service.

931
01:32:18,290 --> 01:32:19,708
Deal or no deal,
Mr. Bridger,

932
01:32:19,791 --> 01:32:22,127
you deserve something
for what you did.

933
01:32:22,461 --> 01:32:23,795
Thank you.

934
