935
01:32:34,097 --> 01:32:37,684
Kid's been beating himself up
awful bad the whole trip.

936
01:32:41,146 --> 01:32:43,190
We all saw
the shape Glass was in.

937
01:32:43,273 --> 01:32:45,817
There was no more
to be done. Right?

938
01:32:46,109 --> 01:32:47,152
FITZGERALD: Yeah.

939
01:32:48,987 --> 01:32:50,155
We all saw him.

940
