963
01:42:05,877 --> 01:42:07,670
(SCOUT SHOUTING IN ARIKARA)

964
01:42:11,883 --> 01:42:14,594
There are traces of a camp...

965
01:42:15,136 --> 01:42:18,181
There are traces of a camp...

966
01:42:18,264 --> 01:42:19,307
(BOTH SPEAKING ARIKARA)

967
01:42:19,390 --> 01:42:20,224
