968
01:42:20,391 --> 01:42:23,561
Entering the moon forest.

969
01:42:23,936 --> 01:42:27,940
Maybe from two days ago.
They are moving east.

970
01:42:28,900 --> 01:42:30,652
Tell the others.

971
01:42:31,319 --> 01:42:34,781
Let's move quickly,
Powaga could be with them!

972
