1000
01:46:06,534 --> 01:46:08,452
FITZGERALD: May I join you?
HENRY: Yes.

1001
01:46:08,703 --> 01:46:09,704
Yeah?

1002
01:46:09,787 --> 01:46:10,788
Yes.

1003
01:46:10,872 --> 01:46:14,709
I was wondering
when we might be
getting paid for that haul.

1004
01:46:14,792 --> 01:46:17,503
'Cause them pelts
we collected

1005
01:46:17,587 --> 01:46:19,297
are still out there,
you know...

1006
01:46:19,380 --> 01:46:20,965
...under a couple foot
of dirt and snow.

1007
01:46:21,048 --> 01:46:23,676
But that ain't
my fault.

1008
01:46:23,759 --> 01:46:25,344
I'm waiting for
Captain Leavenworth

1009
01:46:25,428 --> 01:46:27,138
to arrive
with his army.

1010
01:46:27,221 --> 01:46:29,473
Then we'll have
enough men...

1011
01:46:29,557 --> 01:46:32,268
...to shoot some civilization
into those fucking Arikara

1012
01:46:32,351 --> 01:46:34,061
and get back
our pelts.

1013
01:46:34,145 --> 01:46:36,230
All right. All right.

1014
01:46:36,898 --> 01:46:39,233
When's that supposed
to happen?

1015
01:46:39,567 --> 01:46:40,902
I don't know.

1016
01:46:41,235 --> 01:46:43,404
But until then,
nobody gets paid.

1017
01:46:45,740 --> 01:46:47,742
Listen here, all right?

1018
01:46:48,075 --> 01:46:51,746
I was hired to trap 'em.
I wasn't hired to guard 'em.

1019
01:46:52,079 --> 01:46:56,459
The way I see it,
now you, you got a safe.

1020
01:46:56,626 --> 01:46:58,419
It's probably
full of money.

1021
01:46:58,502 --> 01:47:01,297
You signed a contract
to protect your boss

1022
01:47:01,380 --> 01:47:03,591
and your boss's property.

1023
01:47:04,258 --> 01:47:05,551
And that safe
isn't full anymore.

1024
01:47:05,635 --> 01:47:07,929
It's short about $300.

1025
01:47:08,596 --> 01:47:10,932
What the hell is that
supposed to mean?

1026
01:47:11,265 --> 01:47:13,184
It means,
according to my records...

1027
01:47:13,267 --> 01:47:15,186
...you purchased more goods
on the expedition

1028
01:47:15,269 --> 01:47:17,605
than what you are
owed by the company.

1029
01:47:22,443 --> 01:47:24,612
Now, Happy New Year,
Fitzgerald.

1030
01:47:24,820 --> 01:47:26,697
(UPBEAT FOLK MUSIC
